sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Client App
    participant S as Server API
    participant A as Azure OpenAI
    U->>C: Enter Text for Translation
    C->>S: Send Translation Request
    S->>A: Request Translation
    A-->>S: Return Translated Text
    S-->>C: Send Translated Text
    C-->>U: Display Translated Text
    opt Speech Synthesis
        U->>C: Request Audio
        C->>S: Request Speech Synthesis
        S->>A: Request Audio Generation
        A-->>S: Return Audio Data
        S-->>C: Send Audio Data
        C-->>U: Play Audio
    end
